snippet.title: Michael Jr.
snippet.description:
Michael Jr. brings the funny through stand up comedy, skits, short film, man on the street and a variety of other ways, all-the-while making sure it's good for the whole family. 
You will most certainly laugh, however you may also find that you are also inspired. As Michael Jr. is not just about the jokes...
